Here is how Gen Zs have responded to similar questions:

A. A lot

B. A little

C. Nothing at all

D. Refused

Answer: {'A': '69%', 'B': '17%', 'C': '13%', 'D': '0%'}

B. No, not likely

C. Refused 

Answer: {'A': 65%', 'B': '35%', 'C': '0%'}

C. Refused
